{"id": "kwartaalperspectief-detacheringsbranche-q2-2025__c4-paragraph__0027", "text": "In addition to the developments and opportunities that arise in specific sectors, there are also plenty of current issues that affect all sectors. From climate policy and elections to staff shortages and commodity prices.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "kwartaalperspectief-detacheringsbranche-q2-2025__c4-paragraph__0027", "source_slug": "kwartaalperspectief-detacheringsbranche-q2-2025", "source_title": "Quarterly perspective on the secondment industry Q2 2025", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/alle-sectoren/kwartaalperspectief-detacheringsbranche-q2-2025.html", "source_date": "2025-08-13", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "alle sectoren", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 27, "n_chunks_total": 39, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
